title: Day 9: Hair Raising by Jacobellis and Baumgartner
description:
Lindsey Jacobellis and Nick Baumgartner join us moments before their podium ceremony to talk about signature hairstyles, rad dads and nervous energy.

Follow In The Village on Apple Podcasts for an inside look at the athlete life in Beijing, and watch all the Olympic action unfold on the networks of NBC
author: tess.quinlan@nbcuni.com (NBC Olympics)
